strings: <se_def>Prince Charmles: I say! Where do you think you're going!?
<se_def>Prince Charmles: The royal hunting ground is due east of Argonia. You're going in entirely the wrong direction, you incompetent fool!
<se_def>Prince Charmles: Halt, <leader>! You won't reach the royal hunting ground by going north from here!

<se_def>Prince Charmles: The royal hunting ground is to the EAST!
Now stop this dilly-dallying and take me there at once!
